/p><ul class="OYFlQ DcaPr"><li dir="auto" aria-level="3" class="yOSGR" style="font-size:16px;margin-inline-start:1.5em;list-style-type:square"><p class="-Q4aO hw1z8 DcaPr o-zp-" dir="" id="viewer-q27qu1086913"><span class="ATqq4"><span style="font-size:16px"><span>Range: 3600–5000 (default 4000)</span></span></span></p></li></ul></li></ul></div><div type="bulleted_list" data-hook="rcv-block171"></div><div data-breakout="normal"><div class="-Q4aO hw1z8 DcaPr o-zp-" dir="auto" id="viewer-t21h91077950"><span class="ATqq4"><br role="presentation"/></span></div></div><div type="empty-line" data-hook="rcv-block172"></div><div data-breakout="normal"><p class="-Q4aO hw1z8 DcaPr o-zp-" dir="auto" id="viewer-fdsqq1102771"><span class="ATqq4"><strong style="font-weight:700"><span style="font-size:16px"><span>Pipeline-Specific Notes:</span></span></strong></span></p></div><div type="paragraph" data-hook="rcv-block173"></div><div data-breakout="normal"><ul class="OYFlQ DcaPr"><li dir="auto" aria-level="1" class="yOSGR" style="font-size:16px;margin-inline-start:1.5em;list-style-type:disc"><p class="-Q4aO hw1z8 DcaPr o-zp-" dir="" id="viewer-bd1ye2327259"><span class="ATqq4"><strong style="font-weight:700"><span style="font-size:16px"><span>Built-in &amp; URP:</span></span></strong><span style="font-size:16px"><span> Queue tags are set directly in the shader and appear in the material Inspector.</span></span></span></p></li><li dir="auto" aria-level="1" class="yOSGR" style="font-size:16px;margin-inline-start:1.5em;list-style-type:disc"><p class="-Q4aO hw1z8 DcaPr o-zp-" dir="" id="viewer-v749y2324504"><span class="ATqq4"><strong style="font-weight:700"><span style="font-size:16px"><span>HDRP (2024/2025):</span></span></strong><span style="font-size:16px"><span> Queue tags can be overridden by Material Settings (Rendering Priority). To enforce draw order in HDRP, set the queue in the SubShader tags and adjust Material Order in the Inspector.</span></span></span></p><div class="-Q4a