g style="font-weight:700"><span style="font-size:16px"><span>Grass - </span></span></strong><span style="font-size:16px"><span>For full 3D grass models.</span></span></span></p></li><li dir="auto" aria-level="2" class="yOSGR" style="text-align:AUTO;font-size:16px;margin-inline-start:3.5em;list-style-type:circle"><p class="-Q4aO hw1z8 DcaPr o-zp-" dir="" id="viewer-u0jgt1348411"><span class="ATqq4"><strong style="font-weight:700"><span style="font-size:16px"><span>GrassBillboard - </span></span></strong><span style="font-size:16px"><span>For grass rendered as billboards to improve performance.</span></span></span></p></li></ul></div><div type="bulleted_list" data-hook="rcv-block193"></div><div data-breakout="normal"><div class="-Q4aO hw1z8 DcaPr o-zp-" dir="auto" id="viewer-exhow1322150"><span class="ATqq4"><br role="presentation"/></span></div></div><div type="empty-line" data-hook="rcv-block194"></div><div data-breakout="normal"><div class="Ty9C4" id="viewer-rnpxc143639"><div class="_5TbcM RuCAA"><div class="AWQ51" data-hook="divider divider-dashed" role="separator" aria-orientation="horizontal"><div class="bW26w"><svg class="_95FC7 BkHap oi-6V x4Dgj"><line x2="100%" y1="1" y2="1"></line></svg><div class="vL2Q2"> </div></div></div></div></div></div><div type="divider" data-hook="rcv-block195"></div><div data-breakout="normal"><div class="-Q4aO hw1z8 DcaPr o-zp-" dir="auto" id="viewer-aheyh142468"><span class="ATqq4"><br role="presentation"/></span></div></div><div type="empty-line" data-hook="rcv-block196"></div><div data-breakout="normal"><h4 class="QlafB _16xou DcaPr o-zp-" dir="auto" tabindex="-1" id="viewer-7ztnj1207667"><span aria-hidden="true" id="414-additional-tags-7ztnj120"></span><span class="-kP5W"><span>4.1.4 Additional Tags</span></span></h4></div><div type="heading" data-hook="rcv-block197"></div><div data-breakout="normal"><p class="-Q4aO hw1z8 DcaPr o-zp-" dir="auto" id="viewer-xae0g1208140"><span class="ATqq4"><span style="font-size:16px"><span>Beyond Queue and RenderType, several other tags refine shader behavior:</span></span></span></p></div><div type="paragraph" data-hook="rcv-block198"></div><div data-breakout="normal"><div class="-Q4aO hw1z8 DcaPr o-zp-" dir="auto" id="viewer-o9hcw1211917"><span class="ATqq4"><br role="presentation"/></span></div></div><div type="empty-line" data-hook="rcv-block199"></div><div data-breakout="normal"><ul class="OYFlQ DcaPr"><li dir="auto" aria-level="2" class="yOSGR" style="text-align:AUTO;font-size:16px;margin-inline-start:3.5em;list-style-type:circle"><p class="-Q4aO hw1z8 DcaPr o-zp-" dir="" id="viewer-ngic11224715"><span class="ATqq4"><strong style="font-weight:700"><span style="font-size:16px"><span>RequireOptions - </span></span></strong><span style="font-size:16px"><span>Ensures a pass is rendered only if specific quality settings (e.g., SoftVegetation) are enabled.</span></span></span></p></li><li dir="auto" aria-level="2" class="yOSGR" style="text-align:AUTO;font-size:16px;margin-inline-start:3.5em;list-style-type:circle"><p class="-Q4aO hw1z8 DcaPr o-zp-" dir="" id="viewer-mya441232780"><span class="ATqq4"><strong style="font-weight:700"><span style="font-size:16px"><span>DisableBatching - </span></span></strong><span style="font-size:16px"><span>Controls whether dynamic batching is allowed (values: True, False, LODFading).</span></span></span></p></li><li dir="auto" aria-level="2" class="yOSGR" style="text-align:AUTO;font-size:16px;margin-inline-start:3.5em;list-style-type:circle"><p class="-Q4aO hw1z8 DcaPr o-zp-" dir="" id="viewer-fm9kq1234218"><span class="ATqq4"><strong style="font-weight:700"><span style="font-size:16px"><span>ForceNoShadowCasting - </span></span></strong><span style="font-size:16px"><span>Prevents the shader from casting shadows. (</span></span><strong style="font-weight:700"><span style="font-size:16px"><span>Note:</span></span></strong><span style="font-size:16px"><span> In HDRP, this does not prevent contact shadows.)</span></span></s